  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
            aṟattoṭu niṉṟa tōḻi vatuvai nikaḻāniṉṟuḻit tāykkuk
kāṭṭi uvantu colliyatu. </p>
          <p xml:lang="en">

          </p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Aink103">
              <l> aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai puṉṉaiyoṭu</l>
              <l> ñāḻal pūkkun taṇṇan tuṟaiva</l>
                        <l> ṉivaṭkamain taṉaṉāṟ ṟāṉē</l>
                        <l> taṉakkamain taṉṟivaṇ māmaik kaviṉē</l>
                        
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l> Oh mother, please mother </l>
<l> The man from the cool, pretty harbour </l>
<l> Where Ñāḻal trees bloom along with Puṉṉai trees </l>
<l> Is indeed suitable for this girl </l>
<l> Her great, dark beauty being suitable to him. </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
